{"tid":2008642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華府收緊中国記者簽證規定　港澳人士不受影響","createTime":"2020-05-09T07:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T07:39:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a886df9a5f7eadeb7375493a4d9a9d2816c627e9","tid":2008642,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:33:39.000Z","msg":"美國國土安全部周五（8日）宣布收緊中國記者的簽證規定，回應美國記者在中國所受的對待，指摘中方「打壓新聞獨立」。<br />\n<br />\n新規限制中國記者的簽證有效期為90日，可以申請延長，新例不適用於持香港及澳門護照的記者，將於下周一（11日）生效。此前，記者的簽證沒有限期，除非持有人換了僱主或傳媒機構，否則毋須申請延長。國土安全部一名高官說，新規定讓當局可更頻繁地審查中國記者的簽證申請，或減少派駐美國的中國記者數量，令美國國家安全受到更大保護。<br />\n<br />\n美國月前宣布中國在美國設立的5間國營傳媒為外國使團，北京隨即反擊，驅逐美國3份報章的記者。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200509/mobile/bkn-20200509144301909-0509_00972_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"fc09dcebb5563ef6694ba331387572a2bd6b4f3d","tid":2008642,"uid":41116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"幾多支那人揸住特衰"},{"pid":"28c729d6c08b3d0d540faf38303410403a03048b","tid":2008642,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:34:47.000Z","msg":"限埋澳門啦 根本同支那同氣連枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d83080062583b1f204361f3fbbec5819c1874be","tid":2008642,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:35:32.000Z","msg":"應拒絕xyz人士簽證"},{"pid":"7ef921084a53b590aaa5c4aa06054c5197821681","tid":2008642,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc09dcebb5563ef6694ba331387572a2bd6b4f3d","tid":2008642,"uid":41116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"幾多支那人揸住特衰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:36:25.000Z","msg":"又係時候消費香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee257723dfd696876a42bef5dea271550ec4f4c1","tid":2008642,"uid":121937,"like":0,"dislike